                {
                    "id": "S_f_clamped_by_wind_speed",
                    "description": "Low-wind regime where the min(...) clamp in Eq. 9 selects |V_A|, not S_a*exp(k*|V_A|). At V_A = 0.1 m/s, S_a*exp(k_spread*0.1) = 0.18*exp(0.008424) ≈ 0.18152 m/s, which exceeds |V_A| = 0.1. min(0.18152, 0.1) = 0.1. Exercises the clamp branch of S_f.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {"V_A": 0.1},
                    "initial_conditions": {
